de.tud.kom.p2psim.overlay.bt.algorithm
Interface BTAlgorithmDownloadPeerSelection

All Superinterfaces:
BTAlgorithm
All Known Implementing Classes:
BTAlgorithmDownloadPeerSelectionJustAll
public interface BTAlgorithmDownloadPeerSelection
extends BTAlgorithm

This interface is for a class that selects, which peers should be contacted for downloading, therewith they can be asked for uploading pieces later. It just decides about the handshakes, not about the actual requests.
